android-drawables:unpack

Full name:

com.github.kingamajick.admp:android-drawables-maven-plugin:0.0.1-SNAPSHOT:unpack

Description:

Unpack the bitmap resources contained in one or more 'android-drawables' artifacts.

Attributes:

  • Requires a Maven project to be executed.

Optional Parameters

Name Type Since Description
drawableArtifacts List - A list of DrawableArtifacts to unpack.
unpackLocation File - The location to unpack the drawables too.
Default value is: ${project.build.directory}/android-drawables.

Parameter Details

drawableArtifacts:

A list of DrawableArtifacts to unpack.
  • Type: java.util.List
  • Required: No
  • Expression: ${drawableArtifacts}

unpackLocation:

The location to unpack the drawables too.
  • Type: java.io.File
  • Required: No
  • Expression: ${unpackLocation}
  • Default: ${project.build.directory}/android-drawables
